WEBVTT

00:18.975 --> 00:21.021
[ INDISTINCT WHISPERING ]

00:24.502 --> 00:27.331
[ CRYING ]

00:49.658 --> 00:50.615
[ HEARSE DOOR CLOSES ]

00:50.615 --> 00:53.662
YOU...

00:53.662 --> 00:55.838
YOU DID THIS TO HER.

00:55.838 --> 00:58.971
YOU KILLED MY BABY!

00:58.971 --> 01:02.018
OH, MOM.
[ SOBS ]

01:04.499 --> 01:07.502
[ SOBBING ]

01:07.502 --> 01:09.504
CAN YOU GET MY MOM
IN THE CAR?

01:09.504 --> 01:11.680
OKAY.

01:11.680 --> 01:14.552
[ WHIMPERS ]

01:14.552 --> 01:17.338
I GOT YOU.

01:19.644 --> 01:22.952
[ SNIFFLING ]

01:22.952 --> 01:26.129
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

01:32.657 --> 01:35.834
THE 5-0 JUST CAME BY
TO PAY RESPECT, RIGHT?

01:35.834 --> 01:37.923
CONDOLENCES, BRO.

01:37.923 --> 01:40.491
WE'RE SORRY ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR SISTER.

01:40.491 --> 01:42.580
A LOT OF PEOPLE
TALKING ABOUT IT, HUH?

01:43.755 --> 01:45.409
YOU KNOW ANYTHING?

01:45.409 --> 01:48.238
I KNOW YOU AND ANDY CHAN HAVE
BEEN LOSING SOLDIERS LATELY.

01:48.238 --> 01:51.415
ONLY THING YOU GET
OUT OF GOING TO WAR

01:51.415 --> 01:53.069
IS A BIGGER BODY COUNT.

01:53.069 --> 01:54.418
THAT WHAT
YOU'RE GOING FOR?

01:54.418 --> 01:56.377
