ABOUT A WAR RIGHT NOW.

01:56.377 --> 01:58.422
THIS IS A FUNERAL.

01:58.422 --> 02:00.381
SO IF YOU REALLY
WANT TO PAY CONDOLENCES

02:00.381 --> 02:03.819
AND RESPECT TO MY SISTER,

02:03.819 --> 02:05.821
YOU TELL ME WHAT YOU KNOW
ABOUT HER.

02:05.821 --> 02:07.910
WHAT I KNOW?

02:12.349 --> 02:15.744
YOU CAME AND ROLLED UP ON ME
AT POTRERO.

02:15.744 --> 02:18.355
YOU TOLD ME THAT
YOU KNEW SOMETHING ABOUT HER.

02:18.355 --> 02:20.749
I THINK
YOU MISHEARD ME.

02:20.749 --> 02:22.185
I KNOW
YOU HAD A SISTER.

02:22.185 --> 02:23.926
I DON'T KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT HER, THOUGH.

02:23.926 --> 02:25.319
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

02:25.319 --> 02:27.277
YOU DON'T KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT MY SISTER?

02:27.277 --> 02:29.061
NO.

02:32.108 --> 02:34.589
Fatty B.: YO. CAR'S GOING.
LET'S GO.

02:34.589 --> 02:37.766
YOU DON'T KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT MY SISTER?
NO.

02:45.643 --> 02:47.645
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

02:47.645 --> 02:49.256
[ CAR DEPARTS ]

02:49.256 --> 02:51.258
WHAT THE HELL
IS HE TALKING ABOUT?

02:51.258 --> 02:53.173
I HAVE NO IDEA.

02:54.565 --> 02:56.393
[ SCOFFS ]

03:17.501 --> 03:20.112
SARAH: Hi, it's me.
I'm sorry I haven't called.

03:20.112 --> 03:21.940
I'm not sure
I can do this anymore.

03:21.940 --> 03:25.335
I just need some time
to think about things.

03:25.335 --> 03:26.902
OKAY, SO,
IS IT POSSIBLE

03:26.902 --> 03:28.904
THAT SARAH LEFT THAT VOICEMAIL
FOR HER HUSBAND

03:28.904 --> 03:30.906
BEFORE SHE WAS KILLED,
BUT THE DELIVERY WAS DELAYED?

03:30.906 --> 03:32.908
IF WE WERE TALKING
ABOUT A DAY OR TWO,

03:32.908 --> 03:35.302
THEN MAYBE BECAUSE TECHNOLOGY'S
STILL BASICALLY CRAP

03:35.302 --> 03:36.825
FOR WHAT WE PAY FOR IT,

03:36.825 --> 03:39.480
BUT THREE WEEKS TAKES US
WAY OUT OF GLITCH TERRITORY.

03:39.480 --> 03:41.308
MORE LIKELY
SOMEBODY ELSE SENT THAT MESSAGE

03:41.308 --> 03:43.397
AND THEN FORWARDED IT
TO BRIAN TRAN.

03:43.397 --> 03:45.790
HOW DO YOU FORWARD A MESSAGE?IT'S SIMPLE. THERE'S AN APP.

03:45.790 --> 03:47.618
SO THE BREAKUP WASN'T MEANT
FOR HER HUSBAND?

03:47.618 --> 03:49.751
YOU KNOW I LIKE ME
A GOOD LOVE TRIANGLE.

03:49.751 --> 03:51.013
DO I?OKAY, SO LOOK.

03:51.013 --> 03:53.145
SARAH TRAN HAS A LOVER.

03:53.145 --> 03:56.410
SHE TRIES TO BREAK IT OFF.
LOVER GETS MAD, KILLS HER.

03:56.410 --> 03:58.673
AND THEN WHEN SAID LOVER
REALIZES

03:58.673 --> 04:01.284
THAT HOMICIDE'S INVOLVED,
HE/SHE FORWARDS THE VOICEMAIL

04:01.284 --> 04:03.678
TO PROVE THAT WHAT,
SARAH'S STILL ALIVE?

04:03.678 --> 04:05.201
ANY IDEA
WHO FORWARDED THE MESSAGE?

04:05.201 --> 04:08.030
I TRACED IT TO A BLOCKED NUMBER.
LOOKS LIKE A BURNER.

04:08.030 --> 04:09.423
CAN YOU FIND OUT
WHERE IT CAME FROM?

04:10.424 --> 04:11.903
FOR ME?

04:11.903 --> 04:13.688
I WILL BE TAKING A BATH
IN WARRANTS AND RED TAPE,

04:13.688 --> 04:15.516
BUT I'LL DO MY BEST --
FOR YOU.

04:15.516 --> 04:17.561
LOVE YOU.

04:17.561 --> 04:19.737
THAT'S A LOT OF WORK
TO COVER UP A MURDER.

04:19.737 --> 04:22.740
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT DOES IT REMIND YOU OF?

04:22.740 --> 04:24.568
KALEB'S STAGED SUICIDE.

04:24.568 --> 04:26.788
[ SIGHS ]

04:26.788 --> 04:31.662
TWO COPS
KILLED A FEW WEEKS APART,

04:31.662 --> 04:34.926
BOTH BY SOMEONE WHO WANTED IT
TO LOOK LIKE SOMETHING ELSE.

04:34.926 --> 04:36.754
KALEB WAS SHOT,

04:36.754 --> 04:38.756
BUT TRAN WAS GARROTED
AND THROWN INTO THE BAY.

04:38.756 --> 04:41.193
IT'S TWO COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT M.O.s.

04:41.193 --> 04:42.586
WELL, IT COULD BE
INTENTIONAL, THOUGH,

04:42.586 --> 04:43.848
IF THE KILLER KNOWS
HOW COPS THINK.

04:45.023 --> 04:47.635
OR COULD BE A COP.[ SCOFFS ]

04:47.635 --> 04:50.464
[ SIGHS ]

04:50.464 --> 04:52.335
[ KEYS JINGLE ]

04:52.335 --> 04:55.120
LEAVE KALEB WITH COLD CASE
FOR NOW.

04:55.120 --> 04:56.992
WORK SARAH TRAN.

04:56.992 --> 04:59.211
SEE WHERE IT TAKES YOU,
ALL RIGHT?

04:59.211 --> 05:02.432
YES, SIR.

05:06.871 --> 05:10.571
LOOK, IT'S POSSIBLE
THE KILLER IS IN THIS BUILDING.

05:10.571 --> 05:13.400
WATCH YOUR BACKS.

05:16.751 --> 05:20.189
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

05:20.189 --> 05:22.713
IT SOUNDED LIKE
RAT-TAT-TAT-TAT-TAT.

05:22.713 --> 05:24.193
RAT-TAT-TAT-TAT-TAT.
VERY LOUD, VERY LOUD.

05:24.193 --> 05:26.674
RAT-TAT-TAT-TAT-TAT.

05:26.674 --> 05:29.329
RIGHT OUTSIDE THIS DOOR,
THE KITCHEN, THERE WAS A MAN

05:29.329 --> 05:31.418
WITH A MACHINE GUN
SHOOTING ANOTHER MAN.

05:31.418 --> 05:34.638
OH, COME ON, MAN.
I KNOW YOU GUYS SAW SOMETHING.

05:34.638 --> 05:37.293
NO?
BREAK OVER.
HAVE TO WORK.

05:37.293 --> 05:38.555
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

05:40.992 --> 05:42.298
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

05:42.298 --> 05:43.560
HEY, COMMANDER.
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?

05:43.560 --> 05:45.475
HAVE A SEAT
AND CLOSE THE DOOR.

05:45.475 --> 05:48.435
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:48.435 --> 05:50.393
WORD IS THE NORTENOS
AND SURENOS

05:50.393 --> 05:52.830
ARE CREEPING BACK
INTO INGLESIDE.

05:52.830 --> 05:55.485
NOW, FIELD OPERATIONS
HAS SET UP A TASK FORCE

05:55.485 --> 05:56.834
TO WORK
WITH THE COMMUNITY,

05:56.834 --> 05:58.532
COORDINATE
WITH YOUTH SERVICES UNIT.

05:58.532 --> 06:00.272
I'M REASSIGNING YOU.

06:00.272 --> 06:01.752
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU'RE KIDDING ME, RIGHT?

06:01.752 --> 06:03.711
I KNOW THE TIME YOU PUT IN
WITH POTRERO --

06:03.711 --> 06:07.105
YEAH, A YEAR. ME AND MY CREW.
WHY WOULD YOU DO THIS?

06:07.105 --> 06:08.716
THE LATINO GANGS
ARE A MUCH BIGGER PROBLEM.

06:08.716 --> 06:09.804
IT'S NOT EVEN CLOSE.

06:09.804 --> 06:11.240
COME ON.

06:11.240 --> 06:13.068
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT KIDS
THAT ARE RUNNING ERRANDS

06:13.068 --> 06:14.765
FOR THEIR UNCLES
IN PRISON.

06:14.765 --> 06:16.724
AND THEY'RE KILLING PEOPLE.MOSTLY EACH OTHER.

06:16.724 --> 06:19.161
MEANWHILE,
SUGER CASCADE'S GETTING RICH

06:19.161 --> 06:21.163
SENDING SUPER WEED
TO HIGH-SCHOOL KIDS IN BROOKLYN.

06:21.163 --> 06:22.469
WHAT?
THAT DOESN'T MATTER?

06:22.469 --> 06:23.905
IT MATTERS,
BUT IT'S BEEN A YEAR

06:23.905 --> 06:25.559
AND YOU HAVEN'T EVEN
TOUCHED HIM.

06:25.559 --> 06:29.954
OH, I DIDN'T KNOW I WAS ON
A COMPLETELY ARBITRARY DEADLINE.

06:29.954 --> 06:31.695
EASY, SERGEANT.

06:31.695 --> 06:35.699
LOOK,
I'M JUST SAYING...

06:35.699 --> 06:37.919
CASCADE ISN'T
JUST SOME BANGER.

06:37.919 --> 06:40.878
ALL RIGHT,
HE'S SMART AND CAREFUL.

06:40.878 --> 06:43.315
AND I'M GETTING CLOSE.
I JUST NEED TIME.

06:43.315 --> 06:45.274
THESE THINGS DON'T HAPPEN
ON A SCHEDULE.

06:51.585 --> 06:53.413
SO, ARE YOU JUST
CALLING THE WHOLE THING OFF,

06:53.413 --> 06:55.197
OR ARE YOU BRINGING IN SOMEONE
TO REPLACE ME?

06:55.197 --> 06:57.025
TBD.

06:57.025 --> 06:59.680
I DON'T KNOW.

06:59.680 --> 07:01.333
I DON'T KNOW,
COMMANDER.

07:01.333 --> 07:04.336
I JUST GOT TO SAY,
DUE RESPECT,

07:04.336 --> 07:06.687
YOU GIVE ME A TIP
ON A GROW-HOUSE HIT,

07:06.687 --> 07:09.298
TURNS OUT TO BE WRONG,
I CALL YOU OUT ON IT.

07:09.298 --> 07:11.735
NEXT THING I KNOW,
I'M OFF OF SUGER ALTOGETHER.

07:11.735 --> 07:13.128
WHAT'S GOING ON?

07:13.128 --> 07:14.912
WHAT'S GOING ON
IS YOU'RE STANDING IN

07:14.912 --> 07:17.262
YOUR COMMANDER'S OFFICE, AND
EVEN THOUGH YOU LOOK LIKE THAT,

07:17.262 --> 07:19.613
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
ANY EXTRA LATITUDE WITH ME.

07:19.613 --> 07:21.832
THINGS CHANGE.
SOMETHINGS.

07:21.832 --> 07:23.138
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
LIKE IT.

07:23.138 --> 07:24.966
BUT IF YOU WANT STAY
IN THE GANG UNIT,

07:24.966 --> 07:27.055
YOU'RE EXPECT TO PERFORM
YOUR JOB AS ASSIGNED.

07:27.055 --> 07:28.970
[ SCOFFS ]

07:31.233 --> 07:34.062
[ DOOR OPENS, SLAMS ]

07:34.062 --> 07:36.456
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:37.892 --> 07:40.895
YO.
HEY, RAF.

07:40.895 --> 07:42.810
DID YOU HEAR
THIS BULLSHIT?

07:42.810 --> 07:45.116
WE GOT REASSIGNED
TO INGLESIDE.

07:46.378 --> 07:48.337
WHAT? CRIOLLA DIDN'T
TALK TO YOU?

07:48.337 --> 07:51.906
HE DID.
BUT I'M NOT REASSIGNED.

07:52.994 --> 07:56.214
I WAS COMING TO FIND YOU.IT'S COOL, ZAI.

07:56.214 --> 07:57.825
HEY, SORRY ABOUT --
FINE.

07:57.825 --> 08:00.001
IT'S COOL.

08:00.001 --> 08:02.569
SON OF A BITCH.

08:10.098 --> 08:11.752
SO, YOU REFUSED
TO APOLOGIZE?

08:11.752 --> 08:14.929
YOU DIDN'T SHOW ANY REGRET
OR REMORSE FOR WHAT YOU DID?

08:14.929 --> 08:16.583
IT WASN'T MY FAULT.

08:16.583 --> 08:18.410
DID SOMEBODY
PUT A GUN TO YOUR HEAD

08:18.410 --> 08:20.021
AND TELL YOU TO CALL
MR. HANKINS AN ASSHOLE?

08:20.021 --> 08:21.457
YES.
NO.

08:21.457 --> 08:23.285
WHICH MEANS
IT WASYOUR FAULT.

08:23.285 --> 08:26.723
DO YOU REMEMBER WHAT WE SAID
ABOUT ACCOUNTABILITY?

08:26.723 --> 08:29.596
WHAT ABOUT HANKINS?
HE'S NOT ACCOUNTABLE?

08:29.596 --> 08:31.685
HMM? HE CAN JUST DO
WHATEVER HE WANTS,

08:31.685 --> 08:34.470
SCREW ME OVER ON TESTS,
GET ME IN TROUBLE FOR NO REASON?

08:34.470 --> 08:37.081
I-I-I GOT OPENING STATEMENTS
IN TWO DAYS.

08:37.081 --> 08:39.562
I CAN'T KEEP HAVING
THIS CONVERSATION.

08:39.562 --> 08:42.217
IT'S NOT NO REASON.

08:42.217 --> 08:44.654
YOU DIRECTED PROFANITY
AT YOUR HISTORY TEACHER.

08:44.654 --> 08:46.221
THAT WAS A CHOICE
YOUMADE.

08:46.221 --> 08:48.528
I WAS DRIVEN TO THAT.
THAT WAS NOT A CHOICE.

08:49.920 --> 08:52.706
DAMON WAS SCREWING WITH ME
THE ENTIRE CLASS,

08:52.706 --> 08:55.970
AND NOBODY
DID ANYTHING.

08:55.970 --> 08:57.493
I COULDN'T TAKE IT ANYMORE,
SO I JUST SAID, "STOP."

08:57.493 --> 08:59.364
THAT IS ALL I SAID.

08:59.364 --> 09:01.802
AND THEN HANKINS DECIDES
I'M BEING DISRUPTIVE.

09:01.802 --> 09:03.760
AND THEN IT'S JUST
LIKE DETENTION --

09:03.760 --> 09:06.197
WELL, YOU'RE SUSPENDED NOW.HE WASN'T LISTENING TO ME!

09:06.197 --> 09:11.681
YOU MAY NOT
CALL HIM AN ASSHOLE.

09:11.681 --> 09:14.510
YOU'RE NOT LISTENING TO ME,
EITHER!

09:14.510 --> 09:16.512
WHY DO YOU
DRAG ME DOWN HERE, HUH,

09:16.512 --> 09:19.123
IF YOU DON'T GIVE A SHIT
ABOUT ANYTHING I HAVE TO SAY?!

09:19.123 --> 09:20.995
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.

09:20.995 --> 09:22.649
[ DOOR OPENS ]ARE YOU KIDDING?
YOU KNOW WHAT? LET HIM GO.

09:22.649 --> 09:24.476
WAIT, MICHAEL. MICHAEL.JUST LET HIM GO.

09:24.476 --> 09:25.913
MICHAEL, WAIT.LEAVE ME ALONE!

09:26.827 --> 09:29.394
MICHAEL!
OH, SWEETHEART, SWEETHEART.

09:29.394 --> 09:31.745
ARE YOU OKAY? YOU OKAY?YEAH.

09:31.745 --> 09:33.747
SIR, CAN I HELP YOU
WITH SOMETHING?WE'RE OKAY, THANK YOU.

09:33.747 --> 09:35.923
ARE YOU SURE?WE'RE OKAY, THANK YOU.

09:35.923 --> 09:37.098
OKAY.OKAY, LET'S GO.

09:37.098 --> 09:38.403
YOU OKAY?

09:38.403 --> 09:40.275
[ SCOFFS ]

09:43.060 --> 09:47.108
I HAD NO IDEA
SARAH WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR.

09:47.108 --> 09:51.286
BUT IF YOU'RE SAYING YOU HAVE
SOME SORT OF EVIDENCE...

09:51.286 --> 09:53.375
IT DOESN'T
SURPRISE ME.

09:53.375 --> 09:54.637
WHY NOT?

09:54.637 --> 09:58.815
SHE HAD BEEN DISTANT
THE LAST YEAR.

09:58.815 --> 09:59.947
[ SCOFFS ]

09:59.947 --> 10:01.601
UNDERCOVER WORK
ISN'T EXACTLY

10:01.601 --> 10:03.515
PART OF THE RECIPE
FOR A HEALTHY MARRIAGE.

10:03.515 --> 10:07.215
WHY DIDN'T YOU MENTION THAT
WHEN SHE FIRST WENT MISSING?

10:07.215 --> 10:09.130
I WAS IN DENIAL,
I GUESS,

10:09.130 --> 10:11.523
HOPING FOR
THE BEST-CASE SCENARIO.

10:11.523 --> 10:14.352
BUT NOW YOU'RE ON BOARD
FOR THE WORST?

10:16.833 --> 10:19.793
LOOK, IT'S NO PICNIC
BEING INVOLVED WITH A COP, OKAY?

10:19.793 --> 10:22.665
I SPENT
THE WHOLE MARRIAGE

10:22.665 --> 10:24.841
TALKING MYSELF
INTO BEING OPTIMISTIC.

10:24.841 --> 10:26.756
BECAME SECOND NATURE.

10:26.756 --> 10:28.497
SHE'S NOT
DEAD IN THE STREETS,

10:28.497 --> 10:30.194
SHE'S NOT BORED
WITH OUR LIFE,

10:30.194 --> 10:34.024
SHE'S NOT
SLEEPING WITH SOME OTHER COP.

10:34.024 --> 10:35.722
EVERYTHING'S
TOTALLY FINE.

10:35.722 --> 10:38.594
YOU THOUGHT SHE WAS SLEEPING
WITH ANOTHER COP?

10:40.335 --> 10:42.380
NO, IT'S...

10:42.380 --> 10:44.644
IT'S JUST
A POSSIBLE EXPLANATION.

10:46.558 --> 10:49.779
BUT SHE ALSO
WORKED REALLY HARD.

10:49.779 --> 10:55.959
SHE LOVED BEING A COP,
LOSING HERSELF IN THE CASE.

10:55.959 --> 10:59.963
AS FAR AS I KNEW,
IT WAS THAT.

10:59.963 --> 11:01.965
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

11:07.231 --> 11:10.234
PERSON WHO WAS SUPPOSED TO
KNOW SARAH THE BEST

11:10.234 --> 11:11.540
DIDN'T KNOW HER
AT ALL.

11:11.540 --> 11:13.237
OH, NO, I DON'T THINK
HE'S OUR KILLER.

11:13.237 --> 11:16.197
WE GOT TO FIND A WAY
TO GET INTO THAT WOMAN, THOUGH.

11:16.197 --> 11:18.678
YEAH.

11:18.678 --> 11:21.550
YOU REALLY THINK IT'S THAT BAD
BEING INVOLVED WITH A COP?

11:21.550 --> 11:23.857
I DON'T KNOW.
DEPENDS ON THE COP.

11:23.857 --> 11:26.294
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:26.294 --> 11:27.599
ALL RIGHT,
AND THIS EXTENDS

11:27.599 --> 11:28.600
ALL THE WAY DOWN
TO GAYLEY CENTER?

11:28.600 --> 11:30.472
Man: YEAH, SURE.

11:30.472 --> 11:33.649
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ][ Ringing ]

