TALKING ABOUT?

11:51.275 --> 11:53.321
THIS.

11:53.321 --> 11:56.324
THIS ISN'T A NAME.
IT'S A VERB.

11:56.324 --> 11:58.456
UM, SHE BOGARTED
SOME CUSTOMERS.

11:58.456 --> 12:00.545
SO SHE DOESN'T HAVE
ANY FRIENDS.

12:00.545 --> 12:03.418
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

