COME WITH ME A SEC.
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING.

12:05.855 --> 12:08.292
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

12:10.642 --> 12:12.906
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

