[ LAUGHS ]
COME ON.

12:22.654 --> 12:25.701
I DON'T WANT YOU HERE!
OKAY?! THIS IS MYUNIT!

12:25.701 --> 12:27.355
YOU COME TO WORK DRUNK,
YOUR PAPERWORK --

12:27.355 --> 12:29.052
YOU DON'T KNOW
