12:29.052 --> 12:31.011
OH, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT?!

12:31.011 --> 12:34.449
JESUS CHRIST,
HOW IS THIS MY LIFE AGAIN?!

12:34.449 --> 12:36.712
I HAD ADRINK. ONE.

12:36.712 --> 12:38.192
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

12:38.192 --> 12:40.063
OKAY, JUST TO TAKE
THE EDGE OFF RIGHT NOW.

12:40.063 --> 12:42.849
SERIOUSLY, HILDY,
YOU'RE WRONG ABOUT THIS, OKAY?

12:42.849 --> 12:46.069
AND -- AND -- AND THIS IS REALLY
NOT HELPING MY SITUATION.

12:46.069 --> 12:48.768
WHAT IS
YOUR SITUATION?

12:50.378 --> 12:51.596
WHAT IS GOING ON?

12:51.596 --> 12:54.991
I -- J-JUST LET IT GO.

12:54.991 --> 12:58.690
JUNIOR, I'M NOT --
I'M NOT GONNA JUDGE YOU, OKAY?

12:58.690 --> 13:01.519
YOU'RE MY BROTHER.

13:01.519 --> 13:03.565
TALK TO ME.

13:05.567 --> 13:08.788
LAST VACATION, UH...
OH, KAUAI.

13:08.788 --> 13:13.618
YEAH, IT WAS BACK BEFORE,
UH, MY WIFE GOT SICK.

13:13.618 --> 13:18.449
WE, UH -- WE MADE LISTS OF ALL
THE PLACES THAT WE WANTED TO GO.

13:18.449 --> 13:20.277
HOW FAR DID YOU GET?

13:20.277 --> 13:21.801
KAUAI.

13:21.801 --> 13:24.586
YEAH, THINGS MOVED
PRETTY QUICKLY AFTER THAT.

13:24.586 --> 13:26.414
MY WIFE
LOVED THE CRUISE SHIPS.

13:26.414 --> 13:28.633
OH, CRUISE --
[ LAUGHS ]

13:28.633 --> 13:31.636
EVERY YEAR, SHE'D SAY
LIKE IT WAS NEW IDEA,

13:31.636 --> 13:33.247
"WE SHOULD
GO ON A CRUISE."

13:33.247 --> 13:34.988
[ LAUGHS ]

13:34.988 --> 13:38.295
BAD FOOD, BAD ENTERTAINMENT,
AND THERE'S NO ESCAPE.

13:38.295 --> 13:39.862
[ LAUGHS ]

13:39.862 --> 13:42.604
YEAH, YOU WENT, THOUGH,
DIDN'T YOU? YOU WENT.

13:42.604 --> 13:44.824
BUT NOW THAT
SHE'S GONE,

13:44.824 --> 13:46.869
I THINK ABOUT THEM BOATS
ALL THE TIME.

13:46.869 --> 13:48.392
YEAH.

13:48.392 --> 13:51.221
I BET.

13:51.221 --> 13:52.788
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

13:55.965 --> 13:57.793
EH.

13:57.793 --> 13:59.490
ABOUT TIME
FOR ANOTHER VACATION, HUH?

13:59.490 --> 14:04.147
YEAH,
I CAN'T SEE PAST THE WORK.

14:04.147 --> 14:08.021
DID LIEUTENANT KOTO
GIVE Y'ALL THE KALEB CASE?

14:08.021 --> 14:11.154
HMM.
YOU FIND ANYTHING?

14:11.154 --> 14:14.070
NO, BUT I CAN SEE
WHY IT WENT COLD.

14:14.070 --> 14:18.205
NO PRINTS, NO FORENSICS,
CLEAN AS A WHISTLE.

14:18.205 --> 14:20.860
REMINDS ME OF, UH, WHAT WENT
DOWN ON THE SARAH TRAN CASE.

14:20.860 --> 14:23.427
HOW'S THAT?WELL, IT'S A COVER-UP, TOO.

14:23.427 --> 14:24.733
DAMN.
YEAH.

14:24.733 --> 14:28.302
YOU WANT ME TO DIG DEEPER
ON KALEB?

14:28.302 --> 14:30.478
I CAN KNOCK ON SOME DOORS
IF IT'LL HELP.

14:30.478 --> 14:34.134
MAN, THAT WOULD BE GREAT.
I'D APPRECIATE THAT.

14:35.048 --> 14:39.400
OH, AND, UH,
BOOK THAT CRUISE.

14:39.400 --> 14:40.880
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:45.449 --> 14:46.450
YO.

14:46.450 --> 14:49.714
UH-OH.

14:49.714 --> 14:51.629
I WANT TO SEE
THE GUY YOU HIT.

14:51.629 --> 14:53.762
[ SCOFFS ]
I HIT A WALL.

14:53.762 --> 14:57.635
YEAH. I HEARD THEY
REASSIGNED YOU.

14:59.899 --> 15:01.726
WHAT HAPPENED?

15:01.726 --> 15:03.903
I DON'T WANT TO TALK
ABOUT IT.

15:03.903 --> 15:06.906
ALL RIGHT.

15:06.906 --> 15:08.864
MAYBE LATER?

15:08.864 --> 15:11.519
MAYBE.

15:11.519 --> 15:13.782
MAYBE?

15:17.177 --> 15:20.832
ALL RIGHT, I'LL, UH --
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU A CALL.

15:34.759 --> 15:37.023
HEY.

15:37.023 --> 15:39.242
SO, THE PHONE WAS A BURNER.OKAY.

15:39.242 --> 15:42.463
I'VE GOT A WARRANT IN
FOR THE TRANSACTION I.D. NUMBER.

15:42.463 --> 15:44.073
OKAY, WHAT DOES THAT --
WHAT DOES THAT GIVE US?

15:44.073 --> 15:45.683
PLACE AND TIME OF SALE.[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

15:45.683 --> 15:48.034
IF WE'RE LUCKY, SOME VIDEO
OF THE PERSON WHO BOUGHT IT.

15:48.034 --> 15:50.210
THAT'S IT?
[ CHUCKLES ] I'M KIDDING.

15:50.210 --> 15:52.864
I OWE YOU.
HEY.

15:52.864 --> 15:54.170
HEY,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

15:54.170 --> 15:56.477
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT THE UNION?

15:56.477 --> 16:00.568
UH...NOT MUCH, THAT IT'S,
UH, LIKE A SLUSH FUND.

16:00.568 --> 16:02.265
YEAH,
MY DAD WAS PART OF IT.

16:02.265 --> 16:04.528
HIM AND HIS CRONIES SKIMMING OFF
THE POT, PASSING IT AROUND.

16:04.528 --> 16:06.356
ALL RIGHT, SEEMS STANDARD
FOR BACK IN THE DAY.

16:06.356 --> 16:07.923
WELL, APPARENTLY,
IT'S STILL GOING ON.

16:07.923 --> 16:11.405
THEY BOUGHT MY BROTHER'S
GAMBLING DEBT -- 70 GRAND.

16:11.405 --> 16:14.103
YEAH, AND NOW THEY'RE
SWEATING HIM PRETTY HARD.

16:14.103 --> 16:16.366
THAT'S --
THAT'S BIG MONEY.

16:16.366 --> 16:19.761
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]YEAH, AND HE'S TERRIFIED
ABOUT IT, WHICH IS WEIRD TO ME.

16:19.761 --> 16:22.329
WHY -- WHY WOULD
HE BE TERRIFIED? I MEAN,
THEY'RE COPS, RIGHT?

16:22.329 --> 16:25.723
YOU'RE THE SECOND PERSON
TO MENTION THE UNION THIS WEEK.

16:25.723 --> 16:28.161
KALEB'S SISTER SAID
THAT KALEB AND WALT

16:28.161 --> 16:30.380
BOTH WORKED WITH THE UNION
BEFORE THEY ENDED UP DEAD.

16:32.992 --> 16:36.212
AND IF ANY CRIME
IN OUR HISTORY

16:36.212 --> 16:38.823
HAS MET THE THRESHOLD
FOR CAPITAL PUNISHMENT

16:38.823 --> 16:42.653
AS ESTABLISHED
BY THE WILL OF THE PEOPLE,

16:42.653 --> 16:44.655
IT IS THE CRIME
THAT DUSTIN MAKER COMMITTED

16:44.655 --> 16:46.483
ON THAT SCHOOL BUS.

16:46.483 --> 16:48.572
I DON'T KNOW.
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

16:48.572 --> 16:50.574
HONEY?

16:50.574 --> 16:52.315
ANY THOUGHTS?

16:56.841 --> 16:59.235
HONESTLY, I DON'T KNOW
HOW CAN FOCUS ON THAT.

16:59.235 --> 17:02.238
WELL,
IT -- IT'S MY JOB.

17:02.238 --> 17:04.284
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO,
IGNORE IT?

17:04.284 --> 17:07.026
I THINK
WE SHOULD CALL THE POLICE.

17:09.028 --> 17:11.030
AND I THINK
YOU'RE OVERREACTING, HONEY.

17:11.030 --> 17:13.423
ALL RIGHT,
MICHAEL'S RUN OFF BEFORE.

17:13.423 --> 17:14.990
HE ALWAYS
SCARES YOU TO DEATH,

17:14.990 --> 17:17.601
WHICH, JUST MY OPINION,
IS WHY HE DOES IT,

17:17.601 --> 17:19.168
AND THEN
HE ALWAYS COMES BACK.

17:19.168 --> 17:21.910
SO THIS IS MY FAULT?

17:21.910 --> 17:25.131
NOT EVEN CLOSE
TO WHAT I SAID.

17:25.131 --> 17:29.526
WELL, I'M SORRY.
I HAVE A KNOT IN MY STOMACH.

17:29.526 --> 17:32.051
IT DOESN'T FEEL RIGHT.

17:34.488 --> 17:36.316
PLEASE...

17:36.316 --> 17:39.580
DO NOT CALL THE POLICE
RIGHT NOW.

17:40.798 --> 17:43.410
I'M GOING TO
TAKE A BATH.

17:49.633 --> 17:52.288
[ SCOFFS ]

17:52.288 --> 17:54.290
[ PEN SCRATCHING ]

18:10.263 --> 18:12.091
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

18:18.880 --> 18:21.926
[ SIGHS ]

18:34.896 --> 18:37.290
BACK AWAY
FROM THE DOOR.

18:37.290 --> 18:39.292
Suger:
I'M NOT STRAPPED.

18:45.689 --> 18:47.691
FACE THE WALL.

18:47.691 --> 18:49.693
FACE THE WALL!

18:55.525 --> 18:59.138
WHERE'S YOUR SHADOW?

18:59.138 --> 19:02.750
NO GUN, NO SHADOW.

19:02.750 --> 19:04.752
JUST SUGER.

19:09.670 --> 19:12.673
SO, DOES EVERYONE IN
POTRERO KNOW WHERE I
LIVE NOW, OR JUST YOU?

19:12.673 --> 19:15.371
JUST ME.
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:15.371 --> 19:16.938
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

19:24.337 --> 19:26.382
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

19:26.382 --> 19:31.735
YOUR CRIB...
IT LOOKS JUST HOW I PICTURED IT.

19:31.735 --> 19:33.215
IT'S RAW.

19:33.215 --> 19:35.304
YEAH,
THAT'S HOW I LIKE IT.

19:35.304 --> 19:38.046
ME, TOO.

19:41.615 --> 19:44.792
THIS ISN'T
WHAT YOU CAME HERE FOR.

19:44.792 --> 19:49.231
WE HERE NOW.

19:49.231 --> 19:51.102
YOU LET ME IN.

19:51.102 --> 19:53.409
SO...

19:59.894 --> 20:02.897
I KNOW THE OFFICER
THAT ARRESTED TENEA.

20:02.897 --> 20:06.770
WHO?
IT'S NOT IMPORTANT.

20:06.770 --> 20:08.337
VERACRUZ, WHAT YOU MEAN
IT'S NOT IMPORTANT?

20:08.337 --> 20:10.731
WHAT YOU NEED TO KNOW
WAS THAT OFFICER WAS COMPLAINING

20:10.731 --> 20:12.602
BECAUSE YOUR SISTER
WAS ONLY CARRYING

20:12.602 --> 20:14.648
SIXOUNCES OF COKE
WHEN THEY STOPPED HER.

20:14.648 --> 20:16.737
SIX?

20:16.737 --> 20:18.086
THAT'S A MISDEMEANOR.

20:18.086 --> 20:19.609
SHE SHOULD HAVE WALKED
THAT SAME DAY.

20:19.609 --> 20:23.178
AND THEN SHE GOT ARRAIGNED --
FELONY POSSESSION.

20:23.178 --> 20:24.701
AND THE ARREST REPORT

20:24.701 --> 20:26.399
SAID THAT SHE WAS CARRYING
EIGHTOUNCES.

20:26.399 --> 20:29.053
OVER THE LIMIT.

20:29.053 --> 20:31.665
I WENT TO THE COURTHOUSE
TO LOOK AT THE ARREST REPORT,

20:31.665 --> 20:33.884
BUT IT WAS SEALED.

20:33.884 --> 20:36.713
NO REASON
TO SEAL AN ARREST REPORT

20:36.713 --> 20:39.238
FOR A ROUTINE
POSSESSION BUST.

20:39.238 --> 20:41.979
UNLESS SOMEBODY IS TRYING
TO COVER SOMETHING UP.
YEAH.

20:43.938 --> 20:46.332
SOMEBODY AT 850 WAS TRYING
TO JACK UP YOUR SISTER.

20:46.332 --> 20:47.985
I DON'T KNOW WHO --

20:47.985 --> 20:50.684
WHO ELSE IN 850 GOT THEY DICKS
HARD FOR ME BESIDES YOU?

20:50.684 --> 20:52.686
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:56.255 --> 20:58.692
MY COMMANDER.

20:58.692 --> 21:01.216
CRIOLLA.

21:21.584 --> 21:25.022
WHY DID YOU WAIT SO LONG
TO TELL ME?

21:27.634 --> 21:30.245
I GOT TIRED
OF COVERING SHIT UP.

21:57.272 --> 21:59.405
WHAT'S THIS?
LOOK INSIDE.

22:01.711 --> 22:03.713
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

22:12.418 --> 22:15.203
OH, MY GOD.
70 ON THE DOT.

22:15.203 --> 22:17.640
HOW DID YOU
GET THIS?

22:17.640 --> 22:21.601
DID -- DID YOU, LIKE, BREAK INTO
THE EVIDENCE ROOM OR SOMETHING?

22:21.601 --> 22:25.431
NO. I MOVED
SOME STUFF AROUND.

22:25.431 --> 22:27.650
OH, MY GOD.
LEGALLY.

22:27.650 --> 22:30.305
OKAY. LOOK, I'M...

22:30.305 --> 22:33.308
I'M GONNA GET THIS
BACK TO YOU, OKAY,

22:33.308 --> 22:34.831
WITH WHATEVER INTEREST
YOU WANT.

22:34.831 --> 22:36.964
I DON'T WANT INTEREST.

22:38.748 --> 22:40.228
I WANT YOU
TO TELL ME AND TERRY

22:40.228 --> 22:41.838
EVERYTHING YOU KNOW
ABOUT THE UNION.

22:41.838 --> 22:43.666
OH, JESUS CHRIST.

22:43.666 --> 22:46.495
OH.
WHAT THE HELL FOR?

22:49.411 --> 22:52.632
IT'S NON-NEGOTIABLE.

22:52.632 --> 22:56.070
[ SIGHS ]

22:56.070 --> 22:57.463
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

22:57.463 --> 22:59.465
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

23:09.344 --> 23:11.477
SO,
WHO'S IN THE UNION?

23:11.477 --> 23:13.261
I DON'T KNOW
WHO'S IN THE UNION.

23:13.261 --> 23:14.567
EXCEPT FOR CRIOLLA.

23:14.567 --> 23:16.220
THAT'S THE POINT --
NO ONE KNOWS,

23:16.220 --> 23:17.570
EVEN THE PEOPLE
THAT ARE IN IT.

23:17.570 --> 23:19.049
SO, WHAT?
IT'S LIKE THE MEXICAN MAFIA?

23:19.049 --> 23:20.747
PRETTY MUCH.

23:20.747 --> 23:22.096
WELL, H-HOW DID YOU GET UP
WITH CRIOLLA?

23:22.096 --> 23:24.272
HE RECRUITED ME
WHEN I WAS WORKING VICE.

23:24.272 --> 23:25.578
HE RECRUITED YOU.

23:26.405 --> 23:28.624
[ BUZZER ]

23:28.624 --> 23:30.583
HE RECRUITED YOU
FOR WHAT?

23:30.583 --> 23:32.454
INFORMATION.

23:32.454 --> 23:34.413
ANYTIME THERE WAS A BIG BUST
OR CASH GRAB,

23:34.413 --> 23:35.762
I WOULD LET HIM KNOW.

23:35.762 --> 23:37.372
AND YOU GOT A KICKBACK.

23:37.372 --> 23:38.939
YOU COULD CALL IT THAT.

23:38.939 --> 23:40.984
WHAT SHOULD I CALL IT?
DUMB SHIT YOU LEARNED FROM DAD?

23:40.984 --> 23:42.159
YOU SAID THERE WAS GONNA BE
NO JUDGMENTS, OKAY?

23:42.159 --> 23:43.987
HEY.
HEY, HEY, HEY, JUST...

23:43.987 --> 23:46.033
SO, THE LOAN --
DID CRIOLLA --

23:46.033 --> 23:47.774
DID GIVE -- DID CRIOLLA
GIVE YOU THE LOAN?
NO.

23:47.774 --> 23:49.645
WELL, THEN WHO DID?
[ SIGHS ]

23:49.645 --> 23:51.081
LOOK, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU THINK YOU'RE GONNA DO

23:51.081 --> 23:52.518
WITH THIS INFORMATION, OKAY?JUNIOR...

23:52.518 --> 23:54.345
BUT THESE GUYS --
YOU CANNOT TAKE THEM DOWN.

23:54.345 --> 23:55.825
THEY ARE COVERED
ON EVERY ANGLE.

23:55.825 --> 23:57.566
WALT AND KALEB WERE KILLED
WHILE THEY WERE

23:57.566 --> 23:59.350
WORKING FOR THE UNION, SO CAN
YOU PLEASE HUMOR US HERE?

23:59.350 --> 24:02.005
[ SIGHS ]

24:02.005 --> 24:04.051
I WAS TOLD
TO GO TO THE INVISIBLE HAND

24:04.051 --> 24:05.618
AND ASK
FOR THE V.I.P. ROOM.

24:05.618 --> 24:07.576
STRIP CLUB.
YES.

24:07.576 --> 24:09.535
ALL RIGHT.
WHERE SARAH TRAN
WAS WORKING UNDERCOVER?

24:09.535 --> 24:11.058
OUR OTHER DEAD COP?

24:11.058 --> 24:12.799
THEN WHAT WOULD HAPPEN?

24:12.799 --> 24:14.888
SHOW UP AND WALKED IN THE BACK,
AND THERE'S A GIRL THERE.

24:14.888 --> 24:17.499
WAS SHE A DANCER?SHE DOESN'T DANCE.

24:17.499 --> 24:20.720
SHE JUST ASKED ME WHAT I NEED,
I TELL HER,

24:20.720 --> 24:23.505
COME BACK A COUPLE DAYS LATER,
AND SHE'S GOT 70 GRAND FOR ME.

24:23.505 --> 24:26.116
ALL RIGHT, SO THEN THE UNION
IS USING THE STRIP CLUB

24:26.116 --> 24:27.814
AS A COVER
FOR THEIR BUSINESS,

24:27.814 --> 24:30.077
AND THEY'RE USING THE DANCERS
AS MESSENGERS.

24:30.077 --> 24:32.079
SARAH TRAN GOES UNDERCOVER
AT A STRIP JOINT.

24:32.079 --> 24:33.254
BUT INSTEAD
OF FINDING PROSTITUTION,

24:33.254 --> 24:34.734
SHE FINDS THE UNION?

24:34.734 --> 24:36.605
ALL RIGHT, SO WHAT?
DID -- DID SHE WANT IN?

24:36.605 --> 24:38.389
WAS SHE BLACKMAILING
THE UNION? WHAT?

24:38.389 --> 24:39.739
WAS IT ENOUGH
TO HAVE GOTTEN HER KILLED?

24:39.739 --> 24:42.524
IS IT ENOUGH TO HAVE
GOTTEN HER KILLED?!

24:42.524 --> 24:44.744
I DON'T KNOW!
OKAY, I DON'T KNOW ANY MORE!

24:44.744 --> 24:46.963
DID YOU SEE HER?I SAW HER A COUPLE TIMES,
YEAH.

24:46.963 --> 24:48.922
OKAY, BUT SHE WASN'T
DOING ANYTHING UNUSUAL,

24:48.922 --> 24:51.098
SO I JUST PRETENDED
THAT I DIDN'T SEE HER.

24:51.098 --> 24:52.534
I WANT TO TALK TO THE GIRL
WHO GAVE YOU THE MONEY,

24:52.534 --> 24:53.753
FIND OUT
WHO SHE WAS WORKING WITH.

24:53.753 --> 24:54.971
SHE'S NOT
GONNA TELL YOU ANYTHING.

24:54.971 --> 24:56.712
WHO IS SHE?
HOW DO I FIND HER?

24:56.712 --> 24:58.540
WHO'S THE GIRL, JUNIOR?JUNIOR.

25:00.237 --> 25:03.066
YOU'VE MET HER BEFORE.

25:03.066 --> 25:05.460
IT'S MOLK'S GIRLFRIEND,
ALYSSA, OKAY?

25:05.460 --> 25:07.810
[ SIGHS ]

25:13.424 --> 25:16.079
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

25:16.079 --> 25:17.864
WHAT IS THIS?

25:17.864 --> 25:21.563
ALYSSA,
YOU REMEMBER HILDY.

25:21.563 --> 25:24.697
YEAH, YOUR SISTER.
ANOTHER COP.

25:26.133 --> 25:28.483
MY BROTHER TOLD ME THE TRUTH
ABOUT WHERE YOU GUYS MET.

25:28.483 --> 25:30.224
I-I JUST WANTED TO
TALK TO YOU.

25:30.224 --> 25:33.619
OH, JUNIOR TOLD YOU THE TRUTH?
WELL, THAT WOULD BE A FIRST.

25:35.359 --> 25:38.101
SO THAT WHOLE THING ABOUT
YOU APOLOGIZING WAS BULLSHIT.

25:38.101 --> 25:42.715
YEAH. UH...

25:42.715 --> 25:43.803
SORRY.

25:45.456 --> 25:47.458
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

25:49.852 --> 25:51.462
SIT.

25:58.426 --> 26:00.036
WHAT AM I
DOING HERE?

26:00.036 --> 26:03.692
I HAVE A FEW QUESTIONS
THAT I WANTED TO ASK YOU,

26:03.692 --> 26:05.825
AND I THOUGHT YOU'D PREFER IT
IF I WAS DISCREET.

26:05.825 --> 26:08.915
WELL, I GUESS THAT DEPENDS
ON THE QUESTIONS.

26:08.915 --> 26:10.960
WHO DID YOU
REPORT TO?

26:10.960 --> 26:12.483
EXCUSE ME?

26:12.483 --> 26:14.834
WHO IN THE UNION
DID YOU REPORT TO?

26:14.834 --> 26:17.706
THE UNION? I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

26:17.706 --> 26:19.882
THE PEOPLE WHO GAVE YOU
THE 70 GRAND THAT YOU
GAVE TO MY BROTHER.

26:19.882 --> 26:22.929
LOOK, YOU'RE NOT
GONNA GET ANYTHING FROM ME.

26:24.800 --> 26:27.411
WHAT IF
IT WAS MOLK ASKING?

26:27.411 --> 26:29.500
LEAVE HIM OUT OF IT.

26:29.500 --> 26:31.198
I'D LIKE TO.

26:31.198 --> 26:33.809
HE'S A GOOD MAN, AND HE DESERVES
TO KNOW WHAT YOU'RE INTO.

26:33.809 --> 26:37.465
SO ARE YOU
GONNA TELL ME?

26:37.465 --> 26:39.467
OR AM I GONNA
TELL HIM?

26:39.467 --> 26:43.645
LOOK,
I'M TRYING TO GET OUT.

26:43.645 --> 26:45.299
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE.

26:45.299 --> 26:48.215
ARE YOU SCARED OF WHAT
THEY'RE GONNA DO TO YOU?

26:48.215 --> 26:50.391
TALK TO ME.

26:50.391 --> 26:52.828
I'LL PROTECT YOU.

26:52.828 --> 26:56.789
[ SCOFFS ]
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?

26:56.789 --> 26:59.574
BECAUSE YOU HAVE
NO IDEA.

27:08.844 --> 27:11.804
HMM.
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

27:11.804 --> 27:15.459
HMM.
LAPIS IS TRICKY.

27:15.459 --> 27:18.724
TO SOME, IT'S CALMING.
TO OTHERS, CAN COME OFF AS COLD.

27:18.724 --> 27:20.639
I DON'T THINK
IT'S WORTH THE RISK.

27:20.639 --> 27:22.249
I FEEL RIDICULOUS.

27:22.249 --> 27:24.338
STUDIES SHOW THAT COLORS
HAVE A REAL INFLUENCE ON PEOPLE.

27:24.338 --> 27:28.168
WELL, THE ONLY PERSON I HAVE TO
INFLUENCE IS THE JUDGE.

27:28.168 --> 27:32.172
TRY THE CRIMSON.

27:33.739 --> 27:37.046
AH.
THAT'S PRESIDENTIAL.

27:37.046 --> 27:38.831
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

27:41.529 --> 27:43.531
[ BEEP ]WOMAN: Cassie's on the line.

27:43.531 --> 27:45.272
I THINK YOU'RE GETTING
A LITTLE AHEAD OF YOURSELF.

27:45.272 --> 27:47.970
[ CHUCKLES ]PRESIDENTIAL. [ CHUCKLES ]

27:49.842 --> 27:51.495
HI, SWEETIE.

27:51.495 --> 27:53.106
CASSIE:
[ Crying ] Honey.

27:54.716 --> 27:57.414
WHAT?
WHAT'S WRONG?

27:57.414 --> 27:59.852
THERE'S BEEN A LOCKDOWN
AT MICHAEL'S SCHOOL.

27:59.852 --> 28:01.854
WHAT?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

28:01.854 --> 28:04.552
They haven't said.[ DOOR CLOSES ]

28:04.552 --> 28:06.206
IS MICHAEL OKAY?

28:06.206 --> 28:08.861
I DON'T KNOW.
I STILL HAVEN'T HEARD FROM HIM.

28:08.861 --> 28:12.473
WELL, THE CHRONICLE
JUST SAYS "UNSPECIFIED THREAT."

28:12.473 --> 28:14.301
NO REPORTS
OF ANYONE BEING HURT.

28:14.301 --> 28:17.696
YEAH, I KNOW.
IT'S...JUST --

28:17.696 --> 28:19.262
What?

28:19.262 --> 28:22.309
CASSIE, WHAT?

28:22.309 --> 28:24.224
[ SNIFFLES ]

28:24.224 --> 28:26.052
I'M AFRAID THAT MICHAEL
ISTHE THREAT.

28:30.883 --> 28:33.320
SO, I-I DON'T GET IT.
SO -- SO, YOU -- YOU THINK

28:33.320 --> 28:36.540
THAT SHE'S INVOLVED IN SOME KIND
OF MONEY-LAUNDERING THING?

28:36.540 --> 28:38.455
MOLK, THERE'S NO PROOF
OF MONEY LAUNDERING.

28:38.455 --> 28:40.022
WELL,
WHAT DO YOU HAVE PROOF OF?

28:40.022 --> 28:41.632
TERRY, I MEAN, YOU KNOW,
OBVIOUSLY YOU GOT HER INVOLVED

28:41.632 --> 28:43.243
IN SOME KIND
OF BAIT-AND-SWITCH MANEUVER.

